result.title: Co-prime integers problem
result.content: A set S of integers is said to be pairwise coprime if a and b are coprime for every pair (a, b) of different integers in it. Give array A has N elements (N<=5000) integer numbers, determine the most number elements of set S are selected from A. Input 5 30 2 15 5 6 Output 2 Any hint for me? Sorry my poor English !.
